FBIS3-60427 "jptep001___94034" JPRS-TEP-94-001 Document Type:JPRS Document Title:Epidemiology 4 January 1994 EAST EUROPE POLAND Hepatitis Epidemic Reported in Przemysl Province LD2012173193 Warsaw TV Polonia Network in Polish 1600 GMT 20 Dec 93 LD2012173193 Warsaw TV Polonia Network Language: Polish Article Type:BFN [Text] Hepatitis is raging in Przemysl Province. One person has died in the contagious diseases ward at a hospital in Jaroslaw, and 45 people are being hospitalized suffering of this viral inflammation of the liver. A state of epidemiological alert has been declared in the province. Self-service has been banned in food shops. Unpasteurized milk and its products have been withdrawn from sale. Sanitary measures have been stepped up in nurseries, schools, and canteens.
